平台
    omf             https://github.com/oh-my-fish/oh-my-fish
    fisher          https://github.com/jorgebucaran/fisher



fisher
    installation
        curl -sL https://git.io/fisher | source && fisher install jorgebucaran/fisher
    Quickstart
        fisher install ilancosman/tide                  # install plugin
        fisher install jorgebucaran/nvm.fish@2.1.0      # specific plugin
        fisher install ~/path/to/plugin                 # install plugin from local dir
        fisher update
    Listing plugins
        fisher list
        fisher list \^/                                 # list command also accepts a regular expression to filter the output.
    Updating plugins
        fisher update jorgebucaran/fisher
    Removing plugins
        fisher remove jorgebucaran/nvm.fish@2.1.0       # Remove installed plugins
        fisher list | fisher remove                     # remove everything, including Fisher.


